SpeakEasy the Game
------------------
General information about SpeakEasy: http://speakeasy.tuxfamily.org/
WIKI about SpeakEasy: https://github.com/belkiss/SpeakEasy/wiki
Compiling instructions: http://speakeasy.tuxfamily.org/index.php?pages/Download
GIT repository accessible online : https://github.com/belkiss/SpeakEasy


On windows :
------------
Install GLFW, then add the path to the CMAKE_PREFIX_PATH environment variable,
like that :
"C:\Program Files\GLFW", which is the path containing the include and lib folders.
